HOW TO USE:

1. Copy this folder into your robots workspace, build and source
2. Start roslaunch bitbots_live_tool udp bitbots_live_tool_udp.launch ip:=YOUR_IP port:YOUR_PORT. 
3. Start test_node.py, if you want to send test data.
4. Start roscore and rqt on your computer.
5. Select Live Tool from the Plugins tab.
